Jadi, kamu menolak pendapat kakek?

00:26:31.619 --> 00:26:33.490 line:93%
Kakek pemegang saham utama Distribusi Daeil.

00:26:33.520 --> 00:26:36.659 line:93%
Karena pimpinan terhormat juga berinvestasi di Cheong A Bio

