Ada hal

00:31:53.669 --> 00:31:55.379 line:93%
yang harus kulakukan

00:31:59.079 --> 00:32:00.849 line:93%
sebelum menceraikan dia.

00:32:04.220 --> 00:32:05.720 line:93%
Tunggulah aku, Bu.

